name: I GOT into SWISS FIRST CLASS for FREE... *Here's How*
description:
I managed to get into Swiss First Class... a ticket which would usually cost many thousands of pounds. Come along with me on my journey and see how I managed to sit in this exclusive cabin and how I paid zero to be in there! I also check out the Swiss A340 Business Class cabin and sit in the infamous throne seat. 

My IG: will.luxurytravel
